---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import MergePDF from "../../components/pdf-tools/MergePDF";

const title = "Merge PDF Files Online - Free PDF Combiner";
const description = "Combine multiple PDFs into one unified document. Drag and drop files to reorder them. 100% free and secure client-side merging.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <MergePDF client:load />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-12 text-gray-700">
    <article class="prose prose-slate lg:prose-lg mx-auto">
      <h2>Combine Multiple PDFs into One</h2>
      <p>
        Managing multiple PDF files can be chaotic. Our <strong>Merge PDF Tool</strong> allows you to combine separate PDF documents into a single, organized file. Whether you're merging chapters of a book, invoices for a report, or different parts of a project, we make it easy.
      </p>

      <h2>How to Merge PDFs</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Upload:</strong> Select or drag and drop the PDF files you want to combine.</li>
        <li><strong>Reorder:</strong> Drag the files to arrange them in the exact order you want them to appear in the final document.</li>
        <li><strong>Merge:</strong> Click the "Merge PDF" button to process the files.</li>
        <li><strong>Download:</strong> Save your new, unified PDF document instantly.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Why Use Our PDF Merger?</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8 not-prose">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Easy Reordering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Visual drag-and-drop interface lets you arrange your documents exactly how you want them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Client-Side Processing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">For maximum speed and privacy, files are processed directly in your browser whenever possible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Universal Compatibility</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Works on Windows, Mac, Linux, and mobile devices directly from your web browser.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
      <div class="not-prose space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white border rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Is there a limit to how many files I can merge?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            We don't set a hard limit, but performance depends on your device's memory since we process files in the browser. Merging 10-20 files is usually seamless.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white border rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Can I merge password-protected PDFs?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            You will need to unlock (remove the password from) the PDF files before merging them.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
